<section id="stories" class="section--grey text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h5 class="section--title mb-2">Stories</h5>
                <p>Slowly growing a collection of my startup stores,rants and more.</p>
            </div>
            <%= render partial: "projects/project_card" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="section--white text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <h5 class="section--title">Who is This Gordon Guy</h5>
                <p>The answer to that question is probably best answered with what I'm working on at the time the quesiton is asked. Currently, I'm situated with an exciting, young startup we've dubbed <a href="https://wirkn.com" target="_blank">Wirkn</a>. There I head up the product and engineering team as the company's CPO.</p>
                <p>Ten years ago, I stepped foot on <a href="https://uwaterloo.ca" target="_blank">UWaterloo</a> campus for the first time. With a graphing calculator in one hand and a Big Gulp in the other. I couldn't have been more excited about my future in Mechanical Engineering.<p>
                <p>Little did I know that just one year later I'd be trading my iron ring in for late nights with my trusty MacBook on a beat-up couch, in a colorfully decorated startup office.</p>
                <p>Since then I've helped grow, sell and gracefully bring to a close and a number of startup companies across North Ameria.</p>
                <p>I invite you to enjoy some of my stories and to checkout the hobby projects I've created to keep my development and design skills sharp.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

