    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 mb-3">
                <h5 class="section--title">Hobby Projects</h5>
                <p>
                    Here you'll find some of the hobby projects I've been working on to keep my skills sharp.<br>
                    Please note, I'm using the free tier of Heroku to host these site so they can take up to 30s to load.
                </p>

